cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with image segmentation from referring expressions, which is a task that involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of large-scale text-only datasets, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The proposed method involves machine learning, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with joint vision and language modeling, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
